        {
            "title": "歐爾班在匈牙利歷史性大選中失敗 16年執政生涯結束",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 匈牙利總理<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐爾班\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐爾班;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐爾班\">歐爾班</a>在大選中被一個新崛起的反對黨擊敗，這次歷史性選舉結束了其長達16年的執政生涯，將重塑匈牙利與歐盟、俄羅斯和美國政府之間的關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彼得·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"馬扎爾\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:馬扎爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬扎爾\">馬扎爾</a>所在蒂薩黨勢將在議會中獲得絕對多數席位，將使其能夠兌現大膽的承諾，瓦解歐爾班自詡的「非自由體制」。據布達佩斯選舉辦公室周日公佈的數據顯示，在已統計的90%選票中，蒂薩黨獲得了69%的議會席位，而歐爾班的青民盟僅獲得28%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們共同推翻了歐爾班政權，」馬扎爾在台上對興奮的支持者們說道，他身後是多瑙河和燈火通明的議會大廈。「我們將解放匈牙利，奪回我們的國家。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-051a92e6-5ffe-3194-8d18-e9288f12e940-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐爾班承認敗選，並告訴支持者，這一結果對他來說「很痛苦」。他表示已祝賀馬扎爾獲勝。福林兌歐元匯率延續了數月來的漲勢，升至三年來最高水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現年45歲的馬扎爾曾是執政黨內部人士，過去兩年裡，他以變革的理念激勵了國內民眾。隨著選舉結果陸續公佈，布達佩斯多瑙河沿岸的司機們鳴笛慶祝，民眾也涌上街頭歡慶勝利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一結果對川普和俄羅斯總統普丁都是一次打擊，他們試圖讓歐盟任期最長的總理歐爾班繼續掌權。川普曾多次支持歐爾班，並派副總統JD·范斯在大選前幾天前往布達佩斯為歐爾班助選。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐爾班遇大選勁敵 匈牙利走到延續民粹還是回歸歐盟主流的十字路口</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一結果也標志著歐洲民族主義陣營的挫敗，歐爾班曾是該陣營的開拓者和「歐洲愛國者」(Patriots for Europe)的主要推動力，該黨現在是歐洲議會第三大黨。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hungarians Sweep Away Orban After 16 Years in Seismic Vote (3)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%88%BE%E7%8F%AD%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%88%E7%89%99%E5%88%A9%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%80%A7%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97-16%E5%B9%B4%E5%9F%B7%E6%94%BF%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%AF%E7%B5%90%E6%9D%9F-233529777.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-13 08:17:42",
